ZH: 我需要修改我的作业。
EN: I need to edit my homework.

ZH: 请修改这份文件中的错误。
EN: Please correct the errors in this document.

ZH: 修改密码后，请确保记住新密码。
EN: After changing your password, make sure to remember the new one.

ZH: 这篇文章需要修改一下格式。
EN: This article needs to be edited for formatting.

ZH: 我会修改这张照片，让它看起来更好。
EN: I will edit this photo to make it look better.

ZH: 老师建议我修改段落的逻辑顺序。
EN: The teacher suggested that I rearrange the logic of the paragraphs.

ZH: 你觉得这句话有问题吗？要不要修改？
EN: Do you think there is a problem with this sentence? Should it be edited?

ZH: 他花了很多时间修改这个软件的代码。
EN: He spent a lot of time editing the code for this software.

ZH: 这个网站需要做一些修改才能更好地展示产品。
EN: This website needs some modifications to better showcase the products.

ZH: 我们必须修改原计划，因为遇到了意外。
EN: We need to make changes to the original plan because of unexpected events.

ZH: 请修改这个单词的拼写。
EN: Please correct the spelling of this word.

ZH: 建议修改这项政策以满足员工的需求。
EN: It is suggested to modify this policy to meet the needs of the employees.

ZH: 妈妈会帮我修改这封求职信的语法错误。
EN: My mom will help me correct the grammar mistakes in this cover letter.

ZH: 他坚持不修改这份协议的条款。
EN: He insists on not changing the terms of this agreement.

ZH: 在修改文章之前，要先认真审查内容。
EN: Before editing the article, carefully review the content.

ZH: 需要对系统进行一些修改来解决问题。
EN: Some modifications need to be made to the system to solve the issue.

ZH: 这个建议需要修改才能得到所有人的支持。
EN: This proposal needs to be amended to gain support from everyone.

ZH: 老板建议修改公司的管理制度。
EN: The boss suggested changing the company's management system.

ZH: 修改代码前，请备份原文件。
EN: Before editing the code, make a backup of the original file.

ZH: 已经修改完毕，请查看并确认无误。
EN: The editing is completed, please review and confirm.
